title: City of Chains
description: It's been a couple of months since the last post, but now the page for my current game project, City of Chains, is finally ready. City of Chains is a dystopian sci-fi RPG that offers the player non-linear approaches to situations, such as finding alternate routes through the levels and bypassing combat with the right skillset. In addition, many of the player's in-game decisions have an effect on the world and future events
